<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Christ" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Christ,</orth> the Saviour: <bibl n="shak. r2 4.93" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.93" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 93</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r2 4.93" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 93</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.1.19" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 1, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.2.111" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 111</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.106" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 2, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.214" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 1, 214</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.195" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 195</bibl>. Corrupted to <emph>Chrish</emph> by Captain Macmorris in <bibl n="shak. h5 3.2" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 2</bibl>; see Appendix.
